Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面把答案卡传上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定期考试结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离东日本预赛还剩3天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我对英文的长文很有把握
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道那题是陷阱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸…陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(750,100)\frz270\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\fad(600,600)}第二十一首
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(680,200)\fn@汉仪玄宋 55S\frz270\fad(600,600)}犹见白双袖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(640,280)\fn@汉仪玄宋 55S\frz270\fad(600,600)}飘飘大雪扬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那题假装问时间 其实是问时速 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已经开始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且千早在考试期间 完全没有谈过歌牌的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直在忍耐着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わびぬれば いまはたおなじ なにはなる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相处相思苦 风雨早满城
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}抢到了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是平常的绫濑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要牌被抢走了 明明都会往上或往旁边看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视线没有离开牌面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛水一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛正流动着一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个印象… 放置于身体当中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢！ 居然不等我们就开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫濑快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也跟我比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比 我比 我比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桌子君 也请跟我来比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 稍等 我休息一会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}这次轮到我做读手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 喜欢歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它把新再一次带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从夏季全国大赛过后 她在练习时总是有种焦虑感…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为见到了新？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又在想这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样… 会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}たちわかれ いなばのやまの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下因幡道 松涛闻满山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ゆふされば かどたのいなば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暮色门前降 满田何朦胧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あしのまろやに あきかぜぞふく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摇摇鸣稻叶 芦舍临秋风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ほととぎす なきつるかたを ながむれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曙色朦胧里 数声啼杜鹃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不着做到那种地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类用不着那么完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我没念错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早你没注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在刚才的比赛中 真岛把牌背出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没看牌 随意念出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只在脑子里念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本书上说 这样对背诵的练习很有效…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百首和歌 不分顺序一首也没有重复背出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那是优点也是缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脑袋里装的全是文字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握被念出来的牌是很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不多去感受在竞技线中移动的牌是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用眼睛去看 想象画面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得害羞 所以根本不练习空挥吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把牌跟你之间的距离感记在心中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌需要头脑和身体双方并行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑和身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是想着要快要快…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是手却跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你一起变强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你一起参加东日本预赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要全部记住会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎样赢啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在比赛途中记住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初期配置我只记住一半左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 这样我会害怕失误 不敢抢牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫濑同学～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女帝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到每科的老师那里问过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这次没有不及格的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师那么大声叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王赛的预赛要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 喜欢歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 看这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了配合今天的东日本预赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备了新缝制的袴…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高额头同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高额头同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 这次大赛是跟炎热的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不穿袴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一般的大赛上都会开空调
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这里既不开窗 别说空调了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连换气风扇也不能开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以超热的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那么严格？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为「声音」很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西田呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在楼下 跟翠北歌牌会的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大江同学和驹野也是属翠北歌牌会的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们经常受到他们的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 有很多内情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早正在集中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不错 就这样到第一轮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这里有输给女王20张牌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 须藤前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都三年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用准备考试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一志愿可是国公立大学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易得到了高中选手第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中选手权
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高中选手权得到第一或者第二就能被推荐去有名的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便 成为女王也可以得到推荐去好的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 千早的脑中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞入了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多余的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙个性真差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若宫诗畅据说比现在的名人还要强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象不到赢过她的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我赢过须藤前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那赌一赌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天先败退的一方要剃光头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的光头跟男生的光头不可能一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙绝对不是会当做玩笑就放过你的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把女人的性命竟然一不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}开场仪式要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}各位选手请集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得情绪高涨保持到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做无用的逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}一不小心×N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日正是适宜歌牌的好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与这边同时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近江神宫正在举行西日本预选
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本取得第一名的话 不就是世界第一了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫濑同学成为女王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11月将在这个歌牌会馆举行东西代表决定战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}开始了 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了对战表后请马上就坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的对手是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头发由我保护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇上了棘手的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棘手的对手 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是什么都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}梨理华小朋友 拍一张怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}状态如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}真不愧是大牌选手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}夏季的千叶大赛也得到了第一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立川梨理华 仙台的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟女王一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学四年级就升上A级
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说这孩子就是若宫诗畅的接班人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天才梨理华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理华 缎带整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与无名的你受到的期待方式是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是小学6年级的Speed Star
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说绫濑姐姐的速度超级快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在场外观战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理华加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈在看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天才梨理华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与无名的你受到的期待方式是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原田老师 比赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一轮不战而胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以保持体力太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广史先生也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早在和立川梨理华比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会输给小学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师之前跟千早说过「停止快速取牌」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不还是很快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}千早的武器怎么看都是是直觉敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}难得她正在进步着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}这样做不会抹杀掉难得的长处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}特别对手又是立川梨理华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兮春满地 花开香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かくとだに　えやはいぶきの　さしもぐさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊吹艾草茂 无语苦相思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}干的好 梨理华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}これやこの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远去与相送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みちのくの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纷纷心绪乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}せをはやみ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急流岩上碎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}好轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算整个身体飞出去也十分轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不担心手误
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听觉也非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵有点大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}让我看看你的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常被戏弄 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}耳朵竖起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈帮我把头发梳起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌老师说我的耳朵很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是能够听清楚的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是歌牌还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会比千早更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早从竞技线退后了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かけじやそでの ぬれもこそすれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来去难留住 唯沾衣袖湿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:13:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまはただ　おもひたえなむ　とばかりを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:13:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至此劳空候 无须传消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:12:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}跟读手的呼吸对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ひとづてならで　いふよしもがな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言断痴念 也胜苦相思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}不是快而是正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于做得到的人也许很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而对于我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさそふ あらしのにはの ゆきならで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满院非白雪 风雨催落花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}我在进步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}向着前方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふりゆくものは　わがみなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过眼云烟散 身老叹韶华
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为跟我相像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很清楚梨理华的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あひみての　のちのこころに　くらぶれば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自赴佳期后 相思更转愁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴能和大人们一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称赞「快」时很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}むかしはものを おもはざりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾言怀念苦 始信无来由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}おほけなく うきよのたみに おほふかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦海茫无际 佛前表至诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}空牌 手误了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}虽然看起来梨理华压制了场面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有拉开牌数的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的对手应对得很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪个歌牌会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理华瞄准的牌明显是这张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这张送给她来进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没有瞄准的牌也不能被抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适时地取牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lucky 能对上只有速度快的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 不要再凭速度快来取牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于明白是什么意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理华的情况不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手看起来也不是很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是天才嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早步调不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细一点就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真地比对手就会失误
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速取牌也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速取牌也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能相信老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わがたつそまに すみぞめのそで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不才居比睿 墨袖护苍生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:16:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}しらつゆに かぜのふきしく あきののは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:16:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清秋原野上 白露滚凉风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 「しら」都还没念出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是非常快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗 刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比天才梨理华还要快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}つくばねの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰望筑波岭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}きみがため はるののにいでて わかなつむ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原上采春芽 只为献君尝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ありあけの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰看无情月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手误
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あかつきばかり うきものはなし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断肠唯此时 拂晓与君别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちぎりおきし させもがつゆを いのちにて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纵有空言在 命托原上蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不用那么拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あはれことしの あきもいぬめり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老来惊露冷 今岁逝秋风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}むらさめの つゆもまだひぬ まきのはに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骤雨频频降 枝头露未干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是歌牌还是别的都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能喜欢上某件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能喜欢上自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连对手都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破第一轮了吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广史
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望给千早许多的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是敏锐的直觉 还有局势的读取
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸 准确率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌最重要的是才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是才能也有等级
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这一样是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她需要武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不被女王和现任名人这样的天才击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早姐姐 把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是梨理华的幸运标记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来梨理华不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被称为是若宫诗畅再世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她却没有相当的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 那个女王是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么比较也太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理华刚开始也一定这么被人说过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为绫濑同学具有歌牌的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直将这当做是自己的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不轻易地去碰触
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须藤同学 真不甘心啊 我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}第一轮真是艰苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你不是为了留念才来挑战的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我是A级有出场权 我的目标是成为名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}千早突破了第一轮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}新也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么「要加油」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吃的那么急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也 这个也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都洒出来了 真是太不庄重了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 村尾哥输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 输给了西城大一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按理说是不应该会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村尾两年前还向名人挑战过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最近都没有在练习
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 第一轮赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然南云会的人数不少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有潜力成为名人的却不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后就是你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也只是挑战者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是赢不了名人周防久志的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村尾哥 村尾哥 跟我比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新变厉害了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得在被你超过之前当上名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}千早突破了第一轮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}我也一定要成为东日本的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}新你要成为西日本的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二轮快开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位选手请就位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:29.01,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま  ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:34.14,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}それぞれの道を  見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:39.56,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま  また歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:45.19,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}ふたつの想いが  めぐり会う  その日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:54.45,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}迷いながらも 夢の色重ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:22:00.08,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君を想うからこそ 強くなれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:04.88,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}きっと 終わらせない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:09.97,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま  ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:15.06,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}輝く明日を  見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:20.56,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま  ほら 響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:28.28,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君が教えてくれた歌  この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:29.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻你我两人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:34.14,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望着各自不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:39.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻我又放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:45.19,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}直到两人的思念相邂逅的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:54.45,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在迷惘之中 也不放弃追逐梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:22:00.08,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}正因为我思念你 才能变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:04.88,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}一定 不会就这样结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:09.97,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻你我两人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:15.06,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望着光辉闪烁的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:20.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}于是此刻  你听  歌声响彻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:28.28,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你曾经教会我唱的歌谣  回响于这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8\fad(200,200)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}本字幕由 流云字幕组 制作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8\fad(200,200)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}翻译：柿子 清越 link.n 后期：梅子 嘉儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:29.63,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}帰り道は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.01,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}少し風が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:38.18,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}たわいない会話妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.06,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.77,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}僕ら待ち合わせたあの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:52.15,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:59.99,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:05.33,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:11.13,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.01,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:20.51,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:29.63,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}慢步走过回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.01,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}微风轻轻吹拂着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:38.18,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}闲话家常也异常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.06,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}至今依旧一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.77,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我们常常相约等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:52.15,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你可否仍然记得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:59.99,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}现在我心怀强烈的向往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:05.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}有什么在目标之处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:11.13,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}现在的话似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.01,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}试着伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:20.51,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在梦想的路上终有一天会再度重逢吧